  "title": "Salesforce Technical Architect (Salesforce Cloud / Experience Cloud)",
  "description": "<p>We are seeking an experienced Salesforce Technical Architect (8–9+ years) to lead enterprise-scale Salesforce (Service Cloud–focused) architecture and delivery. The role owns end-to-end solution design, integrations, data architecture, and platform governance, translating business strategy into scalable, secure Salesforce solutions while mentoring teams and guiding technical direction.<br /><br /><strong>Mandatory</strong></p><ul><li>8–9+ years of Salesforce experience with at least 3–5 years in an architectural or technical lead role on enterprise implementations.</li><li>Deep, hands-on experience across core Salesforce clouds (Sales, Service) and Experience Cloud</li><li>Strong Apex, Lightning Web Components (LWC), Visualforce, SOQL/SOSL, and declarative automation experience</li></ul><p><strong>Key Highlights</strong></p><ul><li>Own Salesforce solution architecture, technical standards, and governance across multiple domains</li><li>Design complex integrations (ERPs, data platforms, middleware, REST/SOAP) and scalable data models</li><li>Lead technical discovery, estimation, development oversight, and issue resolution</li><li>Drive best practices for security, CI/CD, performance, and platform scalability</li><li>Produce architecture artifacts and mentor developers and admins</li><li>Partner with business and delivery stakeholders to align solutions with outcomes and ROI</li></ul><p>Required Experience</p><ul><li>8–9+ years Salesforce experience; 3–5+ years in technical lead/architect roles</li><li>Deep expertise in Salesforce Sales & Service Cloud; Experience Cloud required, others a plus</li><li>Strong Apex, LWC, integrations, data modeling, and large-scale data handling</li><li>Experience with CI/CD, DevOps tools, and enterprise security models</li></ul><p>Preferred</p><ul><li>Salesforce CTA or progress toward CTA</li><li>Strong leadership, communication, and Agile delivery experience</li><li>Exposure to CPQ, Marketing Cloud, Commerce Cloud a plus.</li></ul>",
